1. *Nameravam* da sutra ujutro odem u teretanu. (I am planning to go to the gym tomorrow morning.)
2. Sinoć sam *nameravala* da učim, ali sam se umesto toga odlučila da pogledam film. (Last night I intended to study, but instead I decided to watch a movie.)
3. *Nameravam* da kupim novu knjigu kada dobijem platu. (I intend to buy a new book when I get paid.)
4. Da li ti *nameravaš* da dođeš na žurku ovog vikenda? (Are you planning to come to the party this weekend?)
5. Nije mi jasno zašto *nameravaš* da odeš u inostranstvo. (I don't understand why you intend to go abroad.)
6. Oni *nameravaju* da renoviraju stan pre nego što se usele. (They intend to renovate the apartment before moving in.)
7. *Nameravam* da se prijavim na kurs engleskog jezika. (I am planning to enroll in an English language course.)
8. Ukoliko *nameravate* da putujete tokom praznika, preporučujem da rezervišete smeštaj unapred. (If you intend to travel during the holidays, I recommend booking accommodation in advance.)
9. Naši prijatelji *nameravaju* da se venčaju sledećeg leta. (Our friends intend to get married next summer.)
10. Kada *nameravate* da završite svoj diplomski rad? (When do you intend to finish your graduate thesis?)